@startuml

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Utente" as User
box "Frontend (Client)" #LightBlue
    participant "LoginForm" as UI
    participant "NextAuth (Client SDK)" as AuthClient
end box

box "Backend (Server)" #LightYellow
    participant "NextAuth API\n(/api/auth/...)" as NextAPI
end box

box "Database" #LightGreen
    database "PostgresDB" as DB
end box

User -> UI: Inserisce Email, Password
User -> UI: Clicca "Login"
activate UI

UI -> AuthClient: signIn("credentials", {email, password})
activate AuthClient

AuthClient -> NextAPI: POST /callback/credentials
activate NextAPI

note right of NextAPI: Esegue funzione 'authorize()'

NextAPI -> DB: FindUser(email)
activate DB
DB --> NextAPI: User Object (con hash password)
deactivate DB

alt Utente non trovato O Password errata
    NextAPI -> NextAPI: bcrypt.compare(pass, hash) -> False
    NextAPI --> AuthClient: 401 Unauthorized
    AuthClient --> UI: Return Error
    UI --> User: "Invalid Credentials"
else Credenziali Valide
    NextAPI -> NextAPI: bcrypt.compare(pass, hash) -> True
    NextAPI -> NextAPI: Genera JWT Session Token
    NextAPI --> AuthClient: 200 OK + Set-Cookie (Session)
    deactivate NextAPI

    AuthClient --> UI: Success (Redirect URL)
    deactivate AuthClient
    UI -> User: Redirect to /home
    deactivate UI
end

@enduml